如何使用ggplot2?

用局部加权回归散点平滑法观察二维变量之间的关系

2 二维密度图b

library(ggplot2)
data(diamonds)
knitr::kable(head(diamonds),caption="数据概要",align='c')
数据概要
carat cut color clarity depth table price x y z
0.23 Ideal E SI2 61.5 55 326 3.95 3.98 2.43
0.21 Premium E SI1 59.8 61 326 3.89 3.84 2.31
0.23 Good E VS1 56.9 65 327 4.05 4.07 2.31
0.29 Premium I VS2 62.4 58 334 4.20 4.23 2.63
0.31 Good J SI2 63.3 58 335 4.34 4.35 2.75
0.24 Very Good J VVS2 62.8 57 336 3.94 3.96 2.48 
#原始变量关系
ggplot(diamonds, aes(carat,price)) +
geom_bin2d() +
facet_wrap(~cut, nrow = 2)

#y变量取对数
ggplot(diamonds, aes(log(carat),price)) +
geom_point() +
facet_wrap(~cut, nrow = 2)

#x变量取对数
ggplot(diamonds, aes(carat,log(price))) +
geom_bin2d() +
facet_wrap(~cut, nrow = 2)

#都取对数，最终成为线性关系。
ggplot(diamonds, aes(log(carat), log10(price))) +
geom_bin2d(bins = 100) +
facet_wrap(~cut, nrow = 2)

4 模型可视化d

set.seed(711)
x = seq(0, 4, length = 100)
y = -x + jitter(rep(1:5, each = 20), 2)
z = rep(1:5, each = 20)
z <- as.factor(z)
moto <- data.frame(x,y,z)
#ols无控制变量
ggplot(moto, aes(x, y)) +
  geom_point(aes(color = z),size=3) +
  geom_smooth(method='lm',se=F)

4.1 分面e

ggplot(moto, aes(x, y)) +
  geom_point(aes(color = z)) +
  facet_wrap(~z, nrow = 2) +
  geom_smooth(method='lm',se=F)

4.2 分组f

  • 使用modelr包进行模型拟合
#不同组拟合不同的模型

ggplot(moto, aes(x, y,group=z)) +
  geom_point(aes(color = z),size=3) +
  geom_smooth(method='lm',se=F)

library(modelr)
mod1 <- lm(y ~ x + z,data = moto)
grid <- moto %>%
data_grid(x,z) %>%
gather_predictions(mod1)
knitr::kable(head(grid),caption="数据概要",align='c')
Table 4.1: 数据概要
model x z pred
mod1 0.000000 1 0.9381255
mod1 0.000000 2 1.6269070
mod1 0.000000 3 2.4161950
mod1 0.000000 4 3.0396146
mod1 0.000000 5 3.8566872
mod1 0.040404 1 0.9104258 
#不同组拟合同一个模型，控制组z                
ggplot(moto, aes(x, y,group=z)) +
  geom_point(aes(color = z),size=3) +
  geom_line(data = grid, aes(y = pred,x=x),size=0.8,color='blue') +
  ylim(0.5,2)

5.1 数据长宽转换h

  • 使用reshape2进行数据长宽转换。

  • 使用facet_wrap进行分面

facet_grid()介绍

library(reshape2)
long <- melt(china_data, id=c("long", "lat","group"))

library(tidyverse)
library(ggplot2)
ggplot(long, aes(x = long, y = lat, group = group,fill= value)) +
  geom_polygon(colour="brown",size=0.2) +
  scale_fill_gradientn(colours = c("yellow", "red"),na.value = "white",breaks = c(10,20,30,40),limits=c(0,43), guide = "legend") +
  coord_map("polyconic") +  
  facet_wrap(~variable,nrow = 3) +
  xlab('经度') + 
  ylab('纬度') +
  theme(legend.title=element_blank()) #去除图例标题

library(rgdal)
bottom  <- readOGR(dsn = "E:/R_codes/maps/CHN_adm/CHN_adm2.shp",stringsAsFactors=F)
OGR data source with driver: ESRI Shapefile 
Source: "E:\R_codes\maps\CHN_adm\CHN_adm2.shp", layer: "CHN_adm2"
with 345 features

library(ggplot2)
bottomdata <- fortify(bottom)         
x <- bottom@data          
xs <- data.frame(x,id=seq(0:344)-1)        
library(plyr)
china_map <- join(bottomdata, xs, type = "full")          
library(readxl)
fills <- read_excel("E:/R_codes/maps/pointmap/citydis.xlsx")

china_map <- join(china_map,fills, type = "full")   
point <- china_map
point <- na.omit(point)
midpos <- function(x) mean(range(x,na.rm=TRUE)) 
centres <- ddply(china_map,.(NAME_2),colwise(midpos,.(long,lat)))
center <- join(centres,fills, type = "full") 
center  <- na.omit(center)

ggplot(china_map,aes(x=long,y=lat)) + 
  geom_polygon(aes(group = group),fill="white",color="black",size=0.1) + 
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x=long, y=lat, size = freq),data = center, colour = "steelblue") +
  coord_map("polyconic") +
  xlab('经度') + 
  ylab('纬度') +
  theme(legend.title=element_blank()) #去除图例标题
